<br />

<br />
I can now heal 2 ticks over any other Bard my level...so instead of 24hps, I heal for 26hps...
<br />

<br />
I noticed my posts on Charisma has made it to other forums concerning Bards.
<br />

<br />
People, Charisma does indeed affect our Hyme line. Its up to you if you wanna raise it. But don't tell other Noob Bards that Charisma has no effect on Hymes if you never tested it for yourself.
<br />

<br />
I get sooo upset when I see others telling others that Charisma has no effect on our Heals.
<br />

<br />
So for all those looking to start a Bard and are asking the question "Does Char affect my Heals?", the answer is YES. Not much, but it does indeed.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
